  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is a single-center randomized, unblinded, placebo-controlled study to investigate
      the effect of pulmonary rehabilitation in subjects with moderate chronic obstructive
      pulmonary disease (COPD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
